# ADIT Energy Resources Syllabus - Link Accessibility Report
**Date:** November 11, 2025

## Executive Summary
This report documents the accessibility status of URLs referenced in the ADIT Energy Resources Syllabus 2025. Links have been categorized as:
- ‚úÖ **Verified Accessible** - Confirmed working and publicly accessible
- ‚ö†Ô∏è **Likely Accessible** - Domain/organization active, specific page not verified
- ‚ùå **Not Accessible** - Dead link or requires authentication
- üìß **Email Address** - Contact information, not a web link

