## PERMITTED TEXTS

### ‚úÖ VERIFIED ACCESSIBLE

1. **OECD BEPS Reports**
   - Original URL: https://web-archive.oecd.org/2019-06-27/373991-beps-reports-2015-executive-summaries.pdf
   - Status: **Archive version exists, but newer versions available**
   - Current Access: https://www.oecd.org/tax/beps/beps-2015-final-reports.htm
   - Note: BEPS reports have been updated and are available on OECD's main site

2. **OECD Model Tax Convention 2017**
   - Direct URL (Full Version): https://www.oecd-ilibrary.org/taxation/model-tax-convention-on-income-and-on-capital-2017-full-version_g2g972ee-en
   - Direct URL (Condensed Version): https://www.oecd-ilibrary.org/taxation/model-tax-convention-on-income-and-on-capital-condensed-version-2017_mtc_cond-2017-en
   - General OECD iLibrary: www.oecd-ilibrary.org
   - Status: **ACTIVE** - Both full and condensed versions with Commentary available

3. **OECD Transfer Pricing Guidelines 2022**
   - Direct URL: https://www.oecd-ilibrary.org/taxation/oecd-transfer-pricing-guidelines-for-multinational-enterprises-and-tax-administrations-2022_0e655865-en
   - General OECD iLibrary: www.oecd-ilibrary.org
   - Status: **ACTIVE** - 2022 edition (January 2022)

4. **Van Raad: Materials on International, TP and EU Tax Law 2020-2021**
   - Publisher: Leiden International Tax Centre (ITC)
