## ESSENTIAL READING

### ‚úÖ VERIFIED ACCESSIBLE

6. **EU Emissions Trading System**
   - URL: https://climate.ec.europa.eu/eu-action/eu-emissions-trading-system-eu-ets_en
   - Status: **ACTIVE** - Comprehensive, up-to-date resource
   - Last verified: November 2025

7. **World Bank Carbon Pricing Dashboard**
   - URL: https://carbonpricingdashboard.worldbank.org
   - Status: **ACTIVE** - Interactive dashboard fully functional
   - Regularly updated with current data

8. **UN Handbook on Carbon Taxation for Developing Countries (2021)**
   - Direct Download: https://desapublications.un.org/file/918/download
   - Info Page: https://desapublications.un.org/publications/united-nations-handbook-carbon-taxation-developing-countries
   - UN iLibrary: https://www.un-ilibrary.org/content/books/9789210001113
   - Environmental Taxation Resources: www.un.org/development/desa/financing/what-we-do/ECOSOC/tax-committee/thematic-areas/environmental-taxation
   - Status: **ACTIVE** - Free PDF download available
   - Additional workstream documents also available

9. **EY Global Oil and Gas Tax Guide**
   - 2019 URL (from syllabus): www.ey.com/en_gl/tax-guides/global-oil-and-gas-tax-guide-2019
   - Current EY Tax Guides: www.ey.com/en_gl/tax-guides
   - Status: **ACTIVE** - EY tax guides section accessible
   - Note: Guide is updated periodically; 2019 edition may have been superseded. Check EY's tax guides page for latest version

