## NOTES

- **Direct Links Provided**: All major resources now have specific, direct URLs rather than just general website addresses
- **Free Resources Fully Accessible**: OECD, UN, IMF, EU, and World Bank materials all have working direct links
- Many links to commercial publishers now include specific product pages with ISBNs
- Several PDF links from 2010-2017 may have been reorganized but content likely still available
- OECD, UN, EU, and World Bank resources are all publicly accessible and regularly updated
- For exam preparation, verify current permitted texts list with CIOT as links may be updated annually

